146
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:52,479
Selama negosiasi merger,

147
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:56,079
kami sepakat Bank Myungsung menangani penjualan

148
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:58,809
sebagai imbalan penggunaan nama Bank Daehan dan posisi presdir.

149
00:08:58,809 --> 00:08:59,819
Apa?

